<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She's the stunning former WAG known for her fit physique.</p>

<p>And on Sunday, Kyly Clarke showed off her incredible abs in a brown crop top and matching coloured tights on Instagram.</p>

<p>The 38-year-old flaunted her slim figure as she smiled and posed at the gym after completing a workout.</p>

<p>Abs-olutely ripped! Kyly Clarke (pictured) showed off her chiseled abs in a crop top while completing a workout on Sunday</p>

<p>The stunning brunette styled her long locks in a high ponytail and went makeup free for the outing.</p>

<p>Kyly's post comes after her ex-husband Michael Clarke reflected on his life, a year after separating from his wife of seven years.</p>

<p>In a rare interview for The Daily Telegraph's Stellar magazine, the 39-year-old retired Australian cricketer said that he's 'so happy right now' and is 'in a great place'.</p>

<p>'The people who know me know I'm extremely private or try and be as private as I can with my personal life,' he said. </p>

<p>High-profile split: Kyly's post comes after her ex-husband Michael Clarke (pictured) reflected on his life, a year after separating from his wife of seven years</p>

<p>Moving on: He confirmed his relationship with P.E Nation co-founder Pip Edwards (pictured) in July when they were spotted enjoying a romantic vacation in Noosa, Queensland </p>

<p>Michael, who co-parents four-year-old daughter Kelsey Lee with Kyly, went on to reveal that he has been able to maintain a 'wonderful' friendship with his ex-wife.</p>

<p>In July, Michael confirmed his relationship with P.E Nation co-founder Pip Edwards when they were spotted enjoying a romantic vacation in Noosa, Queensland. </p>

<p>Hesitant to provide much insight on his new life with Pip, 40, the radio host did say that he couldn't be happier.</p>

<p>'In regards to me personally? I'm so happy right now. I'm in a great place. That's all I can ask for,' he said. </p>

<p>New life: The 39-year-old retired Australian cricketer said that he's 'so happy right now' and is 'in a great place' </p>

<p>Meanwhile, Michael separated from Kyly in September last year, but only revealed their split in a surprise announcement on February 12.</p>

<p>The Clarkes have said the 'amicable' decision to separate was 'the best course' for their daughter Kelsey Lee. </p>

<p>Reports surfaced that Michael had begun dating Pip after his separation with Kyly became public knowledge.</p>

<p>Family: The Clarkes have said the 'amicable' decision to separate was 'the best course' for their four-year-old daughter Kelsey Lee (pictured) </p>
